Title: Toward Construction of Exact Operator Solution of $A_N$-Toda Field
  Theory
Authors: Y. Takimoto, T. Fujiwara
Comments: 11 pages, latex, no figures
Report-no: IU-MSTP/48
\\
  Quantum $A_N$-Toda field theory in two dimensions is investigated based on
the method of quantizing canonical free field. Toda exponential operator
associated with the fundamental weight $\lambda^1$ is constructed.
